window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From the publishers that brought you<i> A Game of Thrones</i> comes the series that inspired George R.R. Martin’s epic work. </b></p> <p>France became a great nation under Philip the Fair - but it was a greatness achieved at the expense of her people, for his was a reign characterised by violence, the scandalous adulteries of his daughters-in-law, and the triumph of royal authority.</p>"; 
